Top Doctor Urges People Over 50 to Do This One Thing for More Energy

Posted: Monday, October 8th, 2018

“I’ve never seen it this bad,” says Dr. Steven Gundry, one of the world’s leading cardiologists and nutrition researchers — referring to increasing fatigue among Americans over 50.

And this low energy problem, Dr. Gundry stresses, is far more dangerous than most people realize.

“You see, energy isn’t just something that makes you feel alert. What you experience as ‘energy’... is actually a chemical in your body called ATP. It powers all your organs and systems — and keeps you healthy.”

And when your ATP goes down, Dr. Gundry says, health problems go up — like weight gain, frequent illness, concentration problems, accelerated aging, and more.

In an effort to curb the epidemic, he’s now released a groundbreaking at-home energy-restoring protocol to the public — which can be used to combat fatigue, sluggishness, and brain fog at any age.

Dr. Steven Gundry

Award-Winning Cardiologist and Nutrition Researcher

Over the course of his career, Dr. Gundry has become something of a folk hero to fatigued people over 50, having helped thousands feel younger and fresher than they had in years.

However, his new report takes appointments out of the equation, by laying out a proven energy-boosting technique, anyone can easily do at home in minutes.

For people like David —a 66-year-old man who decided to try Dr. Gundry’s energy-boosting protocol after trying to complete a demanding home repair project — the effect was almost immediate.

“Having just started (this) regimen, I’ve noticed I have plenty of energy to execute the work at hand. It’s work better suited for a 30-year-old. I certainly am excited to have energy on this project—which is the only way these projects get done,” he wrote.

Since its release, Dr. Gundry’s inbox has been flooded with stories of people over 50 having the energy to do things they hadn’t done in years—like home projects, long walks, playing with grandchildren, going up and down stairs with ease, or simply being able to concentrate better.

However, he cautions that everyone’s body is different, and individual results from his protocol can vary:

“I can’t speak to your specific situation, and I don’t know exactly what your results will look like. What I can tell you is that this simple energy-boosting protocol has worked wonders for thousands of people. So, I highly recommend giving it a try and seeing how you feel.”
